snippet.title: Planet Protector VR - Gameplay Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Planet Protector VR brings the classic missile defence game to your favourite virtual reality headset! A genre that everybody knows transforms into an enthralling and immersive VR experience! 

Protect your planet across a variety of game modes & special missions. You'll be defending cities throughout the world, famous monuments & landmarks, and defeating a variety of alien invaders! 

This game is coming to Google Daydream, HTC Vive, and Oculus Rift on October 13 2017. GearVR & Windows Mixed Reality editions coming soon.
